  "summary": {
    "zh": "西班牙车手，2005、2006 年两届世界冠军。他终结了舒马赫的五连冠，是 F1 史上最全能的车手之一，职业生涯横跨二十余年仍保持顶尖竞争力。",
    "en": "Spanish driver, two-time champion (2005, 2006). He ended Schumacher's five-year reign and is among F1's most complete drivers, competitive across more than two decades."
